description:
&lt;p&gt;Fixed Term Contract or Secondment until the 30th June 2021, to cover a career break vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The purpose of the role is to provide financial support and advice to budget holders across one of HEE&#39;s regions including budget monitoring, forecasting and variance analysis. The post holder will work as part of a regional financial management team and responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provision of a financial management service to budget holders and Trusts/HEI’s&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure financial performance is accurately reported, in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure reporting mechanisms are maintained in order to deliver efficient and accurate information and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong, up-to-date excel skills with demonstrable evidence of advanced excel use in current/most recent role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manipulation of large datasets and ability to interpret and apply sometimes complex financial models to raw data as prescribed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants will commence at the bottom of Band 6 with a full-time starting salary of £31,365, with pay step increases as after 2 years’ service and 5 years&#39; service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These salaries are offered in accordance with NHS Terms and Conditions and the HEE Pay Progression Policy and are subject to annual cost of living review.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note: Applicants from within the NHS will be offered on a secondment basis only, agreement should be obtained from their employer prior to submitting their application.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you like what you have read and think you have the skills and experience we need then don&#39;t delay, apply today! We get lots of applications for our roles and so we sometimes have to close our posts early. Don&#39;t miss out! &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Christine Wearne&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Financial Controller (South East)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: Christine.Wearne@hee.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
